There is no Primary School at Shottisham.The children in the catchment area are taken by bus to Hollesley Primary School and when old enough,go to Butley Middle School and Farlingaye High School,Woodbridge. A privately owned bus company schedules its timetable in order to transport these children to and from the villages.
Children of{American Personnel} stationed in ther area are taken by bus to the American Base School at { {RAF}.Bentwaters
